they're all still here.

28:00.449 --> 28:01.682
So just take
a deep breath and...

28:01.717 --> 28:04.452
Hey, where you been?
You missed it.

28:04.486 --> 28:06.387
Missed what?

28:06.422 --> 28:08.389
The ambulance just
left with Ben in it.
What?

28:08.424 --> 28:09.524
Yeah, they brought him
out of Adrian's house

28:09.558 --> 28:10.591
on one of those
stretcher things.

28:10.626 --> 28:11.759
What happened?

28:11.794 --> 28:13.628
He went into toxic shock
following a brain aneurysm

28:13.662 --> 28:15.530
or heart attack
or something.

28:15.564 --> 28:17.665
