saying anything.

29:04.354 --> 29:06.355
I just said
I'm happy for you.

29:06.390 --> 29:08.291
I was talking to Amy.

29:08.325 --> 29:11.294
Well, I'm gonna say
what I want to say
when I want to say it.

29:11.328 --> 29:12.595
Then fine, just tell us.

29:12.629 --> 29:15.431
