nothing more
to talk about.

29:34.451 --> 29:35.418
I'm on the pill,
we use condoms,

29:35.452 --> 29:38.488
and we're in love
as much as anyone else.

29:38.522 --> 29:38.855
But I thought
you were going to wait.

29:38.889 --> 29:41.524
Yeah, so?

29:41.558 --> 29:43.359
I thought
you were straight.
Things change.

29:43.393 --> 29:44.627
Don't do that.

29:44.661 --> 29:46.362
Don't use whatever
your mother is going through

29:46.396 --> 29:47.430
as your excuse to
do what you're doing.

29:47.464 --> 29:48.531
If you think you're
doing the right thing

29:48.565 --> 29:50.433
then you don't
need an excuse.

29:50.467 --> 29:51.534
But I suspect
you don't think you're
doing the right thing,

29:51.568 --> 29:53.302
which is why Toby
came and talked to me
and not you.

29:53.337 --> 29:54.570
Well, no one talked to me.

29:54.605 --> 29:56.506
Why didn't you
talk to me about it?

29:56.540 --> 29:57.540
