30:04.515 --> 30:07.617
I just said
that things change.

30:07.651 --> 30:09.385
I just decided
that I wanted to
have sex with Toby,

30:09.419 --> 30:10.520
so I did.

30:10.554 --> 30:12.522
Why?
I just felt like it.

30:12.556 --> 30:14.524
ANNE: But I thought
you two were friends

30:14.558 --> 30:15.391
and that you
wanted to wait until
you were in love

30:15.425 --> 30:17.460
