really mean something.

30:17.494 --> 30:19.562
Hello. I said
I've changed my mind.

30:19.596 --> 30:21.597
He's a nice guy, Ashley,
but you're too young.

30:21.632 --> 30:22.465
You're too young to
be out of high school,

30:22.499 --> 30:24.433
you're too young to
be out on the road,

30:24.501 --> 30:25.635
traveling all over
the country,

30:25.669 --> 30:26.536
you're too young to have
all the freedom you have.

30:26.570 --> 30:30.406
Okay before you
say anything else...

30:30.440 --> 30:32.542
Ashley, do you remember
that cooking school
you applied to in Italy?

30:32.576 --> 30:33.009
Yeah?
No!

30:33.043 --> 30:35.278
You got accepted.

30:35.312 --> 30:36.445
