You don't have any money.

30:36.480 --> 30:37.013
And you're not
giving her any.

30:37.047 --> 30:38.548
Toby would love Italy.

30:41.585 --> 30:45.521
I told you that
I would talk to you
if she got in.

30:45.556 --> 30:47.323
Why didn't you
tell me about Toby?

30:47.357 --> 30:49.192
Because there were
other things going on.

30:49.226 --> 30:50.393
You and your girlfriends
have been busy all day

30:50.427 --> 30:52.261
