you tell Anne and George.

32:13.277 --> 32:14.377
Nice, Nora.

32:14.411 --> 32:15.511
Okay, can we
do this now?

32:15.545 --> 32:17.346
Where's Ashley?

32:17.381 --> 32:17.913
