when you went right back to
school after John was born

33:07.364 --> 33:08.497
and you caught up
with all your classes

33:08.532 --> 33:10.333
and you took that
job at the nursery

33:10.367 --> 33:12.535
and when you
took responsibility
for raising your son.

33:12.569 --> 33:14.603
You're a good mother.

33:14.638 --> 33:17.273
And Ricky, I never thought
I'd be saying this to you,

33:17.307 --> 33:18.407
but you're a good father.

33:19.276 --> 33:21.243
And a good man.

33:21.278 --> 33:23.446
Lot of men
in your situation not only
don't take care of the kid,

33:23.480 --> 33:25.448
